  <!--
    Static sitemap for lang-oria.com. Only canonical indexable URLs
    are listed — tool pages (LearnPage, LearnWordPage, 404) are
    excluded by robots.txt + the noindex meta on <Seo />.

    Blog posts and dynamic content (vocabulary, quiz IDs) are NOT
    listed here because (a) they are noindex by design, and (b)
    including them with thousands of entries would dilute crawl
    priority on the money pages (homepage, language hubs, blog).
  -->
